    <h3 {...{
      "id": "jwt-overview"
    }}>{`JWT Overview`}</h3>
    <p>{`There are two phases for the lifecycle.`}</p>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">{`When signing in`}</li>
    </ol>
    <p><inlineCode parentName="p">{`User ID`}</inlineCode>{` + `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Secret String`}</inlineCode>{` = `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`JSON Web Token`}</inlineCode></p>
    <p>{`In the future, the user can now use this token for future requests.`}</p>
    <ol {...{
      "start": 2
